reviewText: My granddaughters LOVE this DVD when it will play...but after the first couple of months it doesn't play at all any more. And this is the SECOND one to do the same thing. Works for a few months then stops. Don't waste your money.

My two year old son loves this video! He was singing along and clapping. He keeps asking "Where is Billy Jonas?". I love that the kids sing along in normal human voices and I'm not having to listen to dolphin spectrum squeaking.
My daughter and I really enjoyed the songs of Billy Jonas. He is one funny guy.

billy jonas rocks! dance sing and beat on a water drum!

songs you will sing for years to come! we got his CD by mistake in a rafi case and were SO EXCITED for the mix-up! super good tribal fun!!
